Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.24,0:01:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,- Regular, or the special?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.88,0:01:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,- I'm actually looking for someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.05,0:01:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Goes by the name Shiro Wan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.15,0:01:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You ever heard of 'em?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.29,0:01:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard he's a regular around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.48,0:01:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,- Who's askin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.77,0:02:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,- Hey, I'm not some cop\Nif that's what you mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.08,0:02:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I need Shiro for a gig.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.58,0:02:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,We go way back.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.47,0:02:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,- Way back, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.05,0:02:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,So, he's a friend of yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.86,0:02:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,- Hmm, yeah I'd say so.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.94,0:02:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a pretty alright guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.01,0:02:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,- Well, in that case
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.50,0:02:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,you tell that jerk that he\Nbetter not show his ugly face
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.15,0:02:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,in here until he pays\Nme the lien he owes me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.37,0:02:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,- Did I say friend? (laughs)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.06,0:02:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I meant acquaintance.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.36,0:02:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Really, we're just colleagues.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.32,0:02:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyways, thanks for your time buddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.00,0:02:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll just be takin' off now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.55,0:02:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Great start.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.03,0:03:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Heather Shields.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.80,0:03:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, uh hey there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.46,0:03:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm looking for Heather?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.25,0:04:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, pal, I've had a rough day.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.94,0:04:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know where she is or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.86,0:04:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,- Daddy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.81,0:04:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Does he know where mommy is?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.68,0:04:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,- I, uh, (sighs)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.78,0:04:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry to bother you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.04,0:05:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,- You got a lotta nerve\Nshowin' up back here,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.58,0:05:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,unless you brought that idiot with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.69,0:05:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,- How much did Shiro owe you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.43,0:05:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,- Well, I'd say about 16,000 lian.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.41,0:05:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.78,0:05:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, you must be in some serious trouble
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.19,0:05:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,with him if you're payin' off.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.57,0:05:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,- His name is clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.68,0:06:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.17,0:06:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.10,0:06:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.27,0:06:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,- April, wait outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.29,0:06:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.14,0:06:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,- So, what's the truth?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.11,0:06:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,- You know, it's better when it's hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.08,0:06:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,- You know, you're really obnoxious.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.39,0:06:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,- The truth is that\Ntruth is hard to come by.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.76,0:06:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,A story of victory for one person
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.81,0:06:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,is a story of defeat for someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.94,0:06:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,By now your uncle has surely told
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.81,0:07:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Ruby and her friends plenty of stories.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.24,0:07:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,- Well he's never given me a\Nreason to doubt him before.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.82,0:07:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,- That doesn't mean those\Nreasons don't exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.16,0:07:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, you and your\Nteammates might as well
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.59,0:07:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,be the poster children for\Nthe Huntsman Academies.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.86,0:07:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Your motives vary, but you all enrolled
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.26,0:07:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,to try and make the world a better place.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.41,0:07:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's adorable.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.03,0:07:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,- It's what huntsmen and huntresses do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.97,0:07:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,- Not all of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.52,0:07:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Some people are just in it\Nfor the money and the fame,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.40,0:07:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,but there's even more that are just
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.22,0:07:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,looking to grow stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.12,0:07:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Your uncle Qrow and I didn't attend Beacon
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.31,0:07:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,to become huntsmen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.48,0:07:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,We did it to learn how to kill huntsmen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.16,0:07:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Daddy and uncle left that part out, hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.07,0:07:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Aside from the Grimm,\Nhuntsmen were the only ones
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.64,0:07:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,capable of ruining our\Nraids and hunting us down.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.12,0:07:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Our tribe needed a counterforce.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.27,0:08:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,And Qrow and I were the perfect age.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.79,0:08:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The entrance exams were child's play
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.52,0:08:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,compared to what we'd\Nalready been through.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.62,0:08:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,We were good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.42,0:08:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So good that we caught the attention of
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.11,0:08:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Beacon's very own\Nheadmaster, Professor Ozpin.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.41,0:08:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Even after we were put on a team,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.10,0:08:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I could tell he was keeping his eye on us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.80,0:08:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Back then I thought it\Nwas because he knew,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.82,0:08:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,but it was team Stark\Nhe was interested in.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.63,0:08:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,- What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.96,0:08:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,- Constant attention,\Nextra training missions,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.72,0:08:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,turning a blind eye whenever\Nwe happened to break the rules
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.54,0:08:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,and get in to more\Ntrouble than we should've.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.66,0:08:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Sound familiar?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.52,0:08:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,- What's your point?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.45,0:08:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,How much do you know\Nabout Professor Ozpin?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.93,0:08:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,About his past?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.58,0:08:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,- He was a prodigy, one of\Nthe youngest headmasters
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.59,0:08:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,to be appointed to a school.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.63,0:08:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,- Because that's how he planned it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.60,0:08:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Because the man you know as\NOzpin designed those schools
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.02,0:09:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and has followers inside every\Nacademy on Remnant that are
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.53,0:09:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,loyal to him and no one else.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.69,0:09:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,- That doesn't make any sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.31,0:09:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,How could he have... no.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.84,0:09:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would someone even do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.27,0:09:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,- Because old man Oz has a\Ngreat and terrible secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.28,0:09:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Raven] One that could\Nspread fear across the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.66,0:09:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,One that he eventually\Nentrusted to our team,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.48,0:09:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,and once I knew, there was no going back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.43,0:09:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I needed to know more,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.28,0:09:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,but with every new discovery I made,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.41,0:09:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,the more horrifying the world became.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.34,0:09:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,- Okay, then tell us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.05,0:09:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the big secret?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.47,0:09:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What's so crazy that the\Nrest of us don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.93,0:09:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The creatures of Grimm\Nhave a master named Salem.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.58,0:09:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,She can't be stopped, she\Ncan't be reasoned with,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.58,0:09:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,and she will not rest until\Nhumanity crumbles at her feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.35,0:09:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,- What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.24,0:10:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,- You know you two haven't\Neven touched your tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.01,0:10:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,- Why should we believe any of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.60,0:10:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,- Now you're catching on.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.57,0:10:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,So far you've done nothing but\Naccept what others tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.31,0:10:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,But you need to question everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.11,0:10:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise you'll end up\Njust as blind as Qrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.21,0:10:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,And your fool of a father.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.39,0:10:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,- Don't you dare talk\Nabout my family like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.40,0:10:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,- You need to calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.27,0:10:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,- Yang, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.90,0:10:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,- Listen to your friend, Yang.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.23,0:10:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Your teammate's never let you down before.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.78,0:10:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,- You don't know the first\Nthing about my teammates.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.39,0:10:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,About me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.76,0:10:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You were never there, you left us!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.38,0:11:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.20,0:11:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,- I know more than you realize.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.89,0:11:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Not just about you, and not\Njust what I've been told,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.57,0:11:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,but the things I've seen with my own eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.35,0:11:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I know the Grimm have a leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.14,0:11:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I know people who can\Ncome back from the dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.74,0:11:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that magic is real,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.96,0:11:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and I can prove it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.27,0:11:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You said Ty told you\Nall about my semblance.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.81,0:11:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Well I doubt he ever told you
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.41,0:11:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,what Oz did to my brother and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.20,0:11:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,- Go see for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.20,0:11:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,- Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.33,0:12:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,- Yang, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.61,0:12:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,- I'll be fine once we can\Nget her to take us to Ruby.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.33,0:12:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,- It's okay if you're not okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.07,0:12:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,- You didn't believe what she said, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.42,0:12:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,- I ... of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.42,0:12:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, not all of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.86,0:12:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It was crazy, we have the dust semblances,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.44,0:12:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,but I mean there's no such thing as magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.35,0:12:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,- A raven?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.62,0:12:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,- I've seen that bird before.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.21,0:12:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,- Maybe it belongs to your mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.88,0:13:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,- How did you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.20,0:13:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I could explain it to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.33,0:13:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,or you could ask your uncle.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.00,0:13:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,- You're letting us go?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.69,0:13:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,- I'm giving you a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.99,0:13:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay here with me,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.82,0:13:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'll answer all of\Nyour questions and more.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.62,0:13:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We can have a fresh start.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.68,0:13:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Or, you can go back to Qrow
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.13,0:13:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and join Ozpen's impossible\Nwar against Salem,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.75,0:13:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,and meet the same fate as so many others.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.23,0:13:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,But can you really go\Nback to trusting someone
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.53,0:13:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,that's kept so much from you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.66,0:13:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,- All I care about is making\Nsure my sister is safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.15,0:13:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,- Ugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.48,0:14:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yang.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.91,0:14:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,If you side with your\Nuncle, I may not be as kind
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.50,0:14:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,the next time we meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.49,0:14:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,- You weren't kind this time, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.58,0:14:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,- I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.90,0:14:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,- This isn't right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.82,0:14:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I get one or two of 'em, but all of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.37,0:14:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Raven.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.52,0:14:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.84,0:15:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,- Alright, the first\Nbatch is just about done.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.71,0:15:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,- Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.54,0:15:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Now we just need Qrow\Nand we'll be all set.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.02,0:15:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,- Do you really think he's\Ngoing to bring that many people?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.81,0:15:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a lot of food.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.60,0:15:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,- Uh, I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.90,0:15:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But it sounds like we can\Nuse all the help we can get.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.97,0:15:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Qrow] I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.13,0:15:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,- Be right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.59,0:15:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,- You're going to overcook that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.34,0:15:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,- No I'm not, shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.76,0:15:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Qrow] Hey, uh, Ruby?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.46,0:15:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,- I'm coming. (gasps)
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.74,0:15:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine, you take over.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.42,0:15:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,So we didn't know how\Nmany people were coming
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.62,0:15:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,so we just cooked all of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.75,0:15:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,- Yang, I... I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.10,0:15:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I should have stayed, and I\Nshould have talked to you more.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.75,0:15:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I just... I wasn't sure if\Nyou wanted me around and...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.61,0:16:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,- I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.18,0:16:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,- I love you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.64,0:16:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,- Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.71,0:16:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,- Weiss?
